==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Resolutely
<hw>Res"o*lute*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a resolute manner; with
fixed purpose; boldly; firmly; steadily; with perseverance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some . . . facts he examines, some he <qex>resolutely</qex>
denies.</q> <rj><qau>Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Resoluteness</ent>⟦br⟧
